        // Instead, create the DateType instance via reflection with anonymous subclass:

        // Use sun.misc.Unsafe or similar to instantiate abstract class without constructor is complicated and unsafe.

        // Alternative: Use the constructor of DefaultDateTypeAdapter that takes DateFormat and style, instead of DateType

